OL,3,CExeter City players 'in tears' after
OL,4,Cfinal day relegation to League Two
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports on a
OL,7,Fdisappointing end to the season for
OL,8,FExeter City
OL,10,FExeter City boss Matt Taylor said his
OL,11,Fplayers and staff were 'hurting' after
OL,12,Fthe club was relegated on the final
OL,13,Fday of the season.
OL,15,FA 2-1 defeat at home to Bradford City
OL,16,Fsaw the Grecians drop into League Two.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
