OL,3,CExeter City players 'in tears' after
OL,4,Cfinal day relegation to League Two
OL,6,FSpeaking after the match, interim boss
OL,7,FTaylor said: "They're hurting in
OL,8,Fthere, they will have regrets, not
OL,9,Fjust from today, but over the course
OL,10,Fof the season.
OL,12,F"They are devastated, there are tears,
OL,13,Fsome know it's their last game for the
OL,14,Fclub. There are a lot of out of
OL,15,Fcontract players.
OL,17,F"It's painful, but there's a bigger
OL,18,Fpicture in terms of what has happened
OL,19,Fover the past 20 games."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
