OL,3,CExeter City players 'in tears' after
OL,4,Cfinal day relegation to League Two
OL,6,FExeter fans arrived at St James Park
OL,7,Fon Saturday hoping to witness a great
OL,8,Fescape, but Bradford opened the
OL,9,Fscoring after 27 minutes.
OL,11,FAs the rain continued to pour and time
OL,12,Fticked away, Exeter pushed for an
OL,13,Fequaliser.
OL,15,FBut Bradford added a second, and
OL,16,Fdespite a late consolation goal for
OL,17,Fthe Grecians, relegation was confirmed.
OL,19,FMatt Taylor paid tribute to the loyal
OL,20,Fsupport of the home fans.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
