FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1777978995
OL,3,CExeter City players 'in tears' after
OL,4,Cfinal day relegation to League Two
OL,6,F"If only we could reflect our fans in
OL,7,Fpassion, for the the way they support
OL,8,Feach other," he said.
OL,10,F"It never wavers, never has done, and
OL,11,FI don't think it ever will.
OL,13,F"They've not had enough to shout
OL,14,Fabout. We've got to find a way of
OL,15,Fmaking sure we make them proud."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
